OL,3,CMan charged after three women raped in
OL,4,Ccity centre
OL,6,FA man has been charged after to report
OL,7,Fthat they were raped in Manchester
OL,8,Fcity centre.
OL,10,F(GMP) was initially called to a report
OL,11,Fof rape at around 3am on Wednesday 31
OL,12,FJanuary on Mancunian Way, Manchester.
OL,14,FOfficers were then contacted
OL,15,Fthroughout the day about three further
OL,16,Fincidents that happened in the same
OL,17,Farea around the same time.
OL,19,FAn area between the city centre and
OL,20,FArdwick was cordoned off while
OL,21,Finvestigations were carried out.
