OL,3,CMan charged after three women raped in
OL,4,Ccity centre
OL,6,FPolice say Stuart Thomson, 33, of
OL,7,FBuxton Road, Stockport has been
OL,8,Fcharged with three counts of rape, one
OL,9,Fcount of assault and four counts of
OL,10,Fthreats with a bladed article.
OL,12,FHe appeared before Stockport
OL,13,FMagistrates Court on 7 February, where
OL,14,Fhe was remanded in custody ahead of
OL,15,Fhis next court appearance at
OL,16,FManchester Crown Court on 13 March.
OL,18,FPolice say the victims are currently
OL,19,Freceiving specialist care and support.
